data.description: PRICE REDUCED! Looking for a home with short term rental potential? Looking to add your finishing touches to a beautifully built custom home? Conveniently located between Kalispell and Whitefish, in the highly desirable Happy Valley area, this home is will not last long! Call Stephanie Mee (406-249-5202) or your real estate professional today for more information.
